comments: Cauley-Stein (GSW) maintains a legal guarding position and absorbs the contact during the driving shot attempt by Ross (ORL).
Cauley-Stein (GSW) establishes himself in a legal screening position and gives Fultz (ORL) room to avoid the contact.
Birch (ORL) is in a legal guarding position and  retreating when he absorbs the marginal body contact on the during the driving shot attempt by Burks (GSW).
Birch (ORL) establishes himself in a screening position in Burks' (GSW) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Robinson III (GSW) makes marginal contact with Birch (ORL) prior to making clean hand-on-ball contact to block the shot attempt.
Green (GSW) brushes Fultz's (ORL) body during the off-ball screen and the contact doesn't knock him off his defensive path.
Fultz (ORL) maintains a legal guarding position on Bowman (GSW) when he cleanly deflects the pass.
As Green (GSW) commits a take foul on Birch (ORL), he makes incidental foot to foot contact with Isaac (ORL).
As Cauley-Stein (GSW) is trying to establish himself in a screening position, Fultz (ORL) wraps and dislodges him.
Isaac (ORL) makes incidental contact to Robinson III's (GSW) arm after the release that does not affect affect his ability to follow-through naturally.
After Fultz (ORL) and Paschall (GSW) legally jostle for the loose ball on the rebound, Fultz makes contact to Paschall's arm that affects his play at the basket.
After Fournier's (ORL) legal pick, Robinson III (GSW) goes to Fournier's body, but doesn't fully drive through his body as he delivers marginal contact.
Burks (GSW) cleanly dislodges the ball from Fultz (ORL) at the end of his drive to the basket.
Isaac (ORL) delivers a forearm to Green's (GSW) backside and affects his ability to rebound.
Green (GSW) grabs and pulls Birch's (ORL) jersey away from his body off-ball.
Green (GSW) makes contact to Birch's (ORL) body during his shooting motion that affects his play at the basket.
Paschall (GSW) establishes himself in a screening position in Fournier's (ORL) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Birch (ORL) establishes himself in a screening position in Burks' (GSW) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Burks (GSW) maintains verticality as he makes incidental contact with Fournier (ORL) during his driving shot attempt.
Green (GSW) and Birch (ORL) engage and disengage during the rebound on the missed free throw. After a timeout is whistled, both players continue to briefly engage.
Fultz (ORL) commits a take foul on Burks (GSW).
A 5 second violation is correctly whistled prior to Isaac (ORL) and Bowman (GSW) engaging.
Paschall (GSW) and Isaac (ORL) engage and disengage during the inbound.
Green (GSW) firms up in a legal screening position in Iwundu's (ORL) path and absorbs the contact.
Robinson III (GSW) dislodges Gordon (ORL) out of bounds as he gathers the loose ball near the sideline.
